            , Watchman, depos'd, That on Sunday the 3d of Feb. about 2 or 3 in the Morning, he heard a Noise of Pewter, and seeing the Prisoner, he carried her to the Watch-house, where they found the Goods upon her mentioned in the Indictment, that she said they were her own, but the Name on the Pewter not agreeing with her's, the Constable detain'd her till the Prosecutor detected her.</p>
